,
<w canon="ê-mostohtêcik" class="vai" gcat="3pAIcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="simply_walk" stem="mostohtê" suffix="-cik">ê-mostohtêcik</w>
,
<w canon="ê-nitonawâcik" class="vta" gcat="3p3oTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="look_for" stem="nitonaw" suffix="-âcik">êh-nitonawâcik</w>
<w canon="ayahciyiniwa" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="Blackfoot" stem="ayahciyiniw" suffix="-a">iyâhciyiniwah</w>
.
<gloss>At one time he set out from his lodge; nine men were in the party; they went on foot, looking for Blackfoot.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="1.2">
<w canon="kîtahtawê" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="at_times" stem="kêtahtawê">kîtahtawê</w>
<w canon="niyânanwâw" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="five_times" stem="niyânanwâw">niyânanwâw</w>
<w canon="ê-tipiskâyik" class="vii" gcat="0oIIcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="be_night" stem="tipiskâ" suffix="-yik">êh-tipiskâyik</w>
,
<w canon="niyânanwâw" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="five_times" stem="niyânanwâw">niyânanwâw</w>
<w canon="ê-kî-nipâcik" class="vai" gcat="3pAIcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj kî|PAST" sgloss="sleep" stem="nipâ" suffix="-cik">ê-kîh-nipâcik</w>
,
<w canon="mostoswa" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="cattle" stem="mostosw" suffix="-a">mostoswah</w>
<w canon="wâpamêwak" class="vta" gcat="3p3oTA" sgloss="see" stem="wâpam" suffix="-êwak">wâpamêwak</w>
.
<gloss>When five nights had passed and five times they had slept on the way, they saw some buffalos.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="1.3">
<w canon="pêyak" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="one" stem="pêyak">pêyak</w>
<w canon="awa" class="dem" gcat="3sDEM" sgloss="this" stem="awa">awa</w>
<w canon="sipwêhtêw" class="vai" gcat="3sAI" sgloss="leave" stem="sipwêhtê" suffix="-w">sipwêhtêw</w>
,
<w canon="ê-nitawi-pâskiswât" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj nitawi|go_to" sgloss="shoot_at" stem="pâskisw" suffix="-ât">êh-ntawi-pâskiswât</w>
.
<gloss>One man went out to shoot them.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="1.4">
<w canon="ê-nipahât" class="vta" gcat="3s3oTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="kill" stem="nipah" suffix="-ât">êh-nipahât</w>
