<w canon="mostoswa" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="cattle" stem="mostosw" suffix="-a">mostoswah</w>
,
<w canon="ê-wî-nipahâyit" class="vta" gcat="3o3oTAcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj wî|will" sgloss="kill" stem="nipah" suffix="-âyit">êh-wîh-nipahâyit</w>
.
<gloss>Then he saw a great herd of buffalos come forth and saw a large band of Blackfoot coming in pursuit of the buffalo, to kill them.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="1.12">
