,
<w canon="wâpamikoci" class="vta" gcat="3o3sTAsubjunc" sgloss="see" stem="wâpam" suffix="-ikoci">wâpamikoci</w>
<w canon="ta-nipahikot" class="vta" gcat="3o3sTAcnj" preverbs="ta|FUT" sgloss="kill" stem="nipah" suffix="-ikot">ta-nipahikot</w>
.
<gloss>He could not flee, for if they saw him, they would kill him.</gloss>
</seg>

