<w canon="misiwê" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="all_over" stem="misiwê">misiwê</w>
<w canon="nipahêyiwa" class="vta" gcat="3o3oTA" sgloss="kill" stem="nipah" suffix="-êyiwa">nipahêyiwah</w>
<w canon="mostoswa" class="na" gcat="3oNA" sgloss="cattle" stem="mostosw" suffix="-a">mostoswah</w>
.
<gloss>Everywhere in yon direction whence they had come, the others had killed buffalos.</gloss>
</seg>

<seg n="1.17">
<w canon="êkwa" class="ipc" gcat="IPC" sgloss="then" stem="êkwa">êkwah</w>
<w canon="ê-itâpit" class="vai" gcat="3sAIcnj" preverbs="ê|cnj" sgloss="look_there" stem="itâpi" suffix="-t">êh-itâpit</w>
,
